## Purpose
- this dir contains a set of standalone function that implement Cloudflare snippets for the `rhapp.app` domain/zone
- see the official documentation of snippets at: https://developers.cloudflare.com/rules/snippets/

- any file typescript file in this directory that starts with `serve_` describes a snippet



<cli-tools>
cfsnip : a custom tools used to manage snippets
</clitools>

```
cfsnip -h
cfsnip [command]

Commands:
  cfsnip list             list all the snippets                        [default]
  cfsnip get <snippet>    get snippet source
  cfsnip deploy <file>    deploy a snippet                          [aliases: d]
  cfsnip rules <snippet>  list rules for a snippet                  [aliases: r]
  cfsnip rm <snippet>     delete a snippet

Options:
      --version  Show version number                                   [boolean]
  -d, --details  show details                                          [boolean]
  -h, --help     Show help                                             [boolean]
```


